      "message": "a number parameter in a nested yaml file must not have constraints.  A nested yaml can be called by many Heat Orchestration Templates in the VNF, each having different range constraints.  The parameter in the nested yaml file would need to be the min/max of all parameters.  Also, constraints are being enforced by the \"parent\" file.",
